categories: City Navigator Europe Micro SD/SD Card
description: Heading to Europe? Slip this little microSD card into your compatible Garmin GPS to take the mystery out of the streets and highways. For travel on 2 feet, 2 wheels, or 4 tires, it’s like having a local as your guide 24/7.Includes full country coverage for Western Europe and many countries in Eastern Europe as well as French Guiana and the islands of Malta, St. Barthélemy, Martinique, Guadeloupe, and Réunion.Includes more than 10 million kilometres of motorways, national and regional thoroughfares, and local roads.Displays more than 5.5 million restaurants, lodging, border crossings, attractions, gas stations, campsites, shopping and more.Gives turn-by-turn directions on compatible device.With speaker-equipped devices, directions are given out loud, which helps with the pronunciation for local place names.Includes navigational features, such as turn restrictions, roundabout guidance, speed categories and more.Contains traffic data for compatible devices that use traffic receivers.
name: Garmin City Navigator Europe Micro SD/SD Card
